  >   - How to setup `linux performance counters`?
  >     > [`setup.sh`](https://github.com/qlibs/pref/blob/main/.github/scripts/setup.sh)
  >     ```sh
  >     .github/scripts/setup.sh --perf # --rdpmc --max-sample-rate 10000
  >     ```
