  >     PERF_PLOT_TERM='dumb' ./a.out
  >     PERF_PLOT_TERM='dumb size 80,25' ./a.out
  >     PERF_PLOT_TERM='dumb size 150,25 ansi' ./a.out
  >     ```
  >
  >   - How to plot using windows-based charts?
  >     ```sh
  >     PERF_PLOT_TERM='wxt' ./a.out
  >     ```
  >
